                <p>Whether you're joining us for a family dinner, a quick lunch, or ordering online for a special occasion, we're committed to providing exceptional food and service that will keep you coming back.</p>
                <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline-primary mt-3">Learn More About Us</a>
